---
title: Salmon in Lemony Garlic Chive Butter with roast potatoes and broccoli
description: Flaky fried salmon is basted in lemony, herby, garlicky butter in this simple but delicious recipe. Filling golden roast potatoes add a satiating element to this Omega-rich dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R11_W46_IE_IECF12934-6_Mainhigh-fb0dba16.jpg
